---
---

<section class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy-light/50">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-coral font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Who is this for?</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-14">
      Built for people who care where their data lives.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Persona 1: Self-hosters (primary) -->
      <div class="bg-navy border border-coral/20 rounded-xl p-8 relative">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Self-hosters &amp; privacy-first</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Runs on your machine. Your data never leaves. Apache-2.0 licensed. Audit every line. No telemetry you didn't ask for.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Persona 2: Solo devs -->
      <div class="bg-navy border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Solo developers</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Your AI assistant, in your pocket, with real tools and memory that persists. Research, code, automate &mdash; all from the messaging apps you already use.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Persona 3: Teams -->
      <div class="bg-navy border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-muted-light" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Teams &amp; startups</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          A fleet of specialized agents &mdash; research, code review, ops &mdash; coordinated through DAG pipelines with isolated budgets and tool policies.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
